Job:
Saa da no nnuru sum;
 mma Ɔsoro Nyankopɔn nhwehwɛ akyi kwan;
 mma hann biara ntɔ ngu so.

Ma sum ne owusum nnye no mfa;
 ma omununkum nkata so;
 na sum mmunkam ne hann so.

Ma sum kabii nnye saa anadwo no mfa;
 ma wonyi saa anadwo no mfi asranna so
 na wɔmmfa nhyɛ ɔsram biara mu.

Ma nʼanɔpa nsoromma nnuru sum;
 na ɔntwɛn adekyee kwa
 a onhu anɔpawia nsensanee a edi kan no,

Otumfo agyan no wɔ me mu,
 me honhom nom ano bɔre no;
 wɔahyehyɛ Onyankopɔn ahunahuna nyinaa atia me.

“Ɛno nti meremmua mʼano;
 mifi me honhom ahoyeraw mu akasa,
 mefi me kra ɔyaw mu anwiinwii.

“Ɛwɔ mu sɛ midi bem de,
 nanso mimmu me ho;
 abrabɔ afono me.

“Abrabɔ afono me;
 enti mɛka mʼasɛm a meremfa hwee nsie
 na mɛkasa afi me kra yawdi mu.

Wode nnansefo foforo betia me
 na woma wʼabufuw ano yɛ den wɔ me so;
 wʼasraafo tu ba me so bere biara.

Amumɔyɛfo ani befura,
 wɔrentumi nguan;
 na wɔn anidaso bɛdan owu ahomegu.”

Wode nkyehama gu mʼanan;
 wohwɛ mʼanammɔnkwan nyinaa so yiye
 na wode agyiraehyɛde ayeyɛ mʼanammɔn mu.

Woahyehyɛ onipa nkwa nna;
 woahyɛ nʼasram dodow ato hɔ
 na woahyɛ no bere a ɔrentumi ntra.

saa ara na onipa tɔ fam na ɔnsɔre bio;
 enkosi sɛ ɔsoro betwa mu no, nnipa rensɔre
 na wɔrennyan wɔn mfi wɔn nna mu.

Ɔrenguan sum no;
 ogyaframa bɛhyew ne mman,
 na Onyankopɔn anom ahomegu bɛsoa no akɔ.

Onyankopɔn tow hyɛ me so tetew me wɔ nʼabufuw mu
 na ɔtwɛre ne se gu me so;
 nea ɔne me anya no pɔkyere nʼani hwɛ me.

Nnipa bue wɔn ano di me ho fɛw;
 wɔbɔ me sotɔre de bu me animtiaa
 na wɔka wɔn ho bɔ mu de tia me.

Na biribiara kɔ yiye ma me, nanso ɔdwerɛw me;
 osoo me kɔn mu, tow me hwee hɔ.
 Ɔde me asi nʼani so;

Nʼakofo ba anibere so;
